<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ạ̹lh ạltʿwyḍạt ʿwḍ kl ạlly fạt
 wbdl ạlạ̉ḥzạn bfrḥ wyạ ạlslạm
 wsẖạl kl ạlậlạm ạ̹lh ạltʿwyḍạt
 1- mạfysẖ wạḥd yjy lh yqfl fy wsẖh ạlbạb
 wlạ wạḥd bynạdy lh hạysybh fy ạlʿdẖạb
 ḥbh wḥnyth bqlbh wrqth fy ạlḥạl hạysmʿ lh
 wyʿwḍ ạlly fạt
 2- mạfysẖ wạḥd ḥzyn tʿbạn wdmʿth
 btsyl ʿly̱ ạlkẖdyn hạysybh fy mḥnth
 ḥbh wḥnyth bqlbh wrqth fy ạlḥạl hạysmʿ lh
 wyʿwḍ ạlly fạt</lyrics>
